    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>欢迎来到 Toon Toon Racing!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/64b6f1a738ad17fb0cf4c036705c38dd.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>利用 SIMCADE 机制掌握具有挑战性的赛道，在现实主义和街机乐趣之间取得完美平衡。 Toon Toon Racing 易于学习，但难以掌握，为那些寻求真正赛车体验的人提供易于上手但具有挑战性的游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>在不同的场景中比赛！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/e1dd46434177b24ff961b578ac8c058e.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>无论是惊心动魄的弯道还是惊心动魄的直道，每场比赛都是脱颖而出并赢得胜利的机会。选择你的赛车，感受肾上腺素的飙升，准备好体验你一生中最激动人心的比赛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>探索我们的车库！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.poster.avif?t=1767982231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.webm?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/70aeda78c43889de20e6d78806c52aaf.mp4?t=1767982231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Toon Toon Racing 提供了一个充满令人难以置信的车辆的车库供您选择！从灵活的经典车型到坚固耐用的超快机器，每辆车都有自己的个性和驾驶风格，准备在游戏充满活力的赛道上脱颖而出。   <br>  <br>加入我们的 Discord 社区！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319260/extras/910076392a195ce2c6b29242cfed0a74.avif?t=1767982231\" width=616 height=338 /></span>想要了解最新的 Toon Toon Racing 新闻吗？交流驾驶技巧、分享您的成就，甚至提出游戏的新想法？我们的社区正在等待您！</p>",
